# Portfolio V3 — Deployment

Do **not** edit plan files. For UI/data conventions see [`v3-design-system.mdc`](v3-design-system.mdc), [`v3-components.mdc`](v3-components.mdc), etc.

## Architecture

| Piece | Location |
|-------|----------|
| V3 (active) | `src/v3/` — entry via [`src/pages/Index.js`](src/pages/Index.js) → `src/v3/containers/Portfolio/Portfolio.js` |
| V2 (legacy) | `src/containers/Portfolio/` — not the active entry |
| Build output | `npm run build` → `build/*` copied to `docs/` |
| GitHub Pages | [`.github/workflows/static.yml`](.github/workflows/static.yml) on push to `main` |
| Custom domain | [`public/CNAME`](public/CNAME) → `carlmanuel.com` (copied into `docs/` on build) |
| Redirect | `carlxaeron.github.io` → `carlmanuel.com` |
| Contact API | [`src/mapping.js`](src/mapping.js) → Firebase Cloud Functions |
| CORS origins | [`functions/index.js`](functions/index.js) — must include `carlmanuel.com` / `www` |

## Pre-push checklist

1. **Tests:** `CI=true npm test -- --watchAll=false --passWithNoTests`
2. **Production build:** `CI=true npm run build` — `CI=true` treats ESLint warnings as errors
3. **Version:** bump `package.json` version for releases
4. **CHANGELOG:** add entry under [`CHANGELOG.md`](CHANGELOG.md) (see 3.0.0 format)
5. Fix ESLint before push: unused imports, missing hook deps
6. Confirm `docs/` reflects build (committed if repo tracks deploy artifacts)

## Git workflow

1. Feature branch → commit → merge to `main`
2. Push `main` → triggers GitHub Actions deploy
3. Tag: `git tag -a vX.Y.Z -m "Release vX.Y.Z" && git push origin main --tags`
4. Create GitHub Release (`gh release create vX.Y.Z --notes-file CHANGELOG.md` or UI)

## GitHub Actions (`.github/workflows/static.yml`)

On push to `main` or `workflow_dispatch`:

1. `npm ci`
2. `npm run build` with secrets injected:
   - `REACT_APP_apiKey`, `REACT_APP_authDomain`, `REACT_APP_projectId`
   - `REACT_APP_storageBucket`, `REACT_APP_messagingSenderId`
   - `REACT_APP_appId`, `REACT_APP_measurementId`
3. Upload `docs/` artifact → deploy to GitHub Pages

**Troubleshooting**

| Symptom | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| ESLint fails in CI | Run `CI=true npm run build` locally; fix warnings |
| `npm ci` 404 | Do not re-add removed deps (`react-particles`, `tsparticles-preset-firefly`) |
| Analytics missing | Add GitHub repo secrets; [`src/config.js`](src/config.js) skips Firebase init when `REACT_APP_projectId` is unset |
| Contact form CORS | Deploy functions after updating allowed origins in `functions/index.js` |

## Firebase functions (when CORS/backend changes)

```bash
cd functions && npm run deploy
```

Deploy copies `src/external-config.js` into `functions/` then runs `firebase deploy --only functions`.

## Post-deploy verification

- `https://carlmanuel.com` — V3 loads, sections/hash nav work, contact form submits
- `https://carlxaeron.github.io` — redirects to custom domain
- Chrome DevTools MCP or `curl -I` for status/redirect headers

